Game itself could be a great sport but the scene is filled with hackers. It doesn't help that companies behind counter-strike have never really done anything about it. Too good of a business that players buy new accounts due bans every now and then. Also it is really hard to start as a new guy. There is also a lot of OG's who've been here since early 2000's. I would choose another FPS game for a better sport as a beginner. There is a lot more potential in some other games. This game won't change unless it is going VR some day.
